{
  "stem": "1415.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all you have to do is step into the middle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he gave us this speech.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I stepped in the middle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I-- during those years in the camp, I had a little girl that was from our hometown.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- during that last part, she attached herself to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was younger than me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she attached herself to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And no matter what I did, she did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when I stepped in the middle, she stepped in the middle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, my-- my light bulb went up in my head, and I said, how do they know who my family is?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if I tell them, maybe I jeopardize-- and this all went up in my head in-- in a matter of seconds.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm talking about seconds, not minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- as I stepped in, almost simultaneously, she stepped in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And almost simultaneously after she stepped in, I stepped back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, it was like, dum, bum, bum, because a light bulb went up in my head saying, how do they know who my family is?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if I-- if I do this, no, it's not good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's preservation.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stepped back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I tried to make her see to step back too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She just stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She just stood there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he kept on talking out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And quite a few of the children stepped in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took them away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, we later found their bodies right outside after liberation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And don't forget, this was winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And their bodies were intact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were right outside-- out-- out-- outside the camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they were shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was towards the end.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
